# Welcome to my mind!
Current interest: Category Theory, Quantum Computation, Non-commutative Geometry, et cetera...
Languages: 中文, English, Deutsch, Português, Español, Русский, עברית, Latim, Euskara, Nahuatl, Yucatecan, Suomi, Svenska, Français, et cetera...

## Free projects
[lisqp](https://github.com/AugustusHuang/lisqp/) A Quantum LISP-like programming language.  
[uxxx](https://github.com/AugustusHuang/uxxx/) A POSIX compatible real-time OS kernel for fun.  
[cl-cs](https://github.com/AugustusHuang/cl-cs/) A Common Lisp Compressed Sensing utility package.  
[cl-hmm](https://github.com/AugustusHuang/cl-hmm/) A Common Lisp HMM package.
